name: micro
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "micro" %}
{% set version = "2.0.8" %}

package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  git_url: https://github.com/zyedidia/micro.git
  git_rev: v{{ version }}
  # url: https://github.com/zyedidia/micro/archive/refs/tags/v{{ version }}.tar.gz
  # sha256: 3e1b7483aa2afffa8afc2c710e22541961ac3de5e026efb4bdddc8ade00d4de0

build:
  skip: true  # [not linux]
  number: 1

requirements:
  build:
    - {{ compiler('go') }} >=1.15
    - go-licenses
    - make

test:
  commands:
    - micro --version

about:
  home: https://micro-editor.github.io/
  license: MIT
  license_file: LICENSE
  summary: 'A modern and intuitive terminal-based text editor'
  dev_url: https://github.com/zyedidia/micro

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - dhirschfeld
